<br>
If it could be stickied that would be nice, as very slight<br>
modifications can and will be made for Plane raid, HOT, etc.<br>
I am currently running ideas with my cohorts and the officers<br>
to work on a better way to distribute non-armor loot, giving<br>
up on the /random method as well I hate it.<br>
<br>
MM<br>
<br>
------------------------------------------------------------------ <br>
<br>
Kael arena drops the NODROP armor pieces that you need for<br>
Thurgadin Quest Armor. It is superior to Plane of Hate/Fear armor,<br>
and of lower quality to Skyshrine and Kael quest armor from TOV.<br>
<br>
Loot will be handled as Class Random, Last piece rule in effect.<br>
<br>
What this means: When a piece of armor drops, any and all who<br>
need it may roll. Example: Chain Boots drop. Any who need <br>
may enter the roll, all ranger/rogue/shaman. Whoever wins<br>
that piece may not win again, unless all in that armor class<br>
have won something already, and the cycle restarts.<br>
<br>
Last Piece Rule: If the 1 piece dropping will complete your<br>
set of Thurgadin quest armor, it is defaulted to you with no roll. If 2 or more people call Last piece on the same item, it <br>
will be randomed between them. To confirm Last Piece Rule, <br>
link your entire set of armor to the Raid Leader (me) BEFORE<br>
the raid starts. <br>
<br>
For Thurgadin armor, you may also include any pieces of armor<br>
from Skyshrine, Kael, or Plane of Growth towards your Last piece.<br>
<br>
Example: Shaman X has a BP and Helm from POG, bracers and<br>
boots from Skyshrine, and Arms and Gloves from Thurgadin quest.<br>
If Chain Legs drop in the arena, he is permitted to claim Last piece,<br>
provided he has linked the entire set to the Leader before the raid.<br>
<br>
I realize some of this is quite confusing, if you have questions<br>
PLEASE ask them in /tells and i will talk it through with you.<br>
<br>
As of now, Last Piece is in effect for the following people:<br>
Alyssta - full set thurgadin - Last Piece Claimed : Plate BP<br>
Morphail - full set thurg. - Last Piece Claimed : Silk Robe<br>
Jilcey - full set thurg. - Last Piece Claimed : Silk Robe<br>
